Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动 燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动 燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…And so, we met in the deep\Ndark and shattered place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no one will come to us. They\Nleft us here with disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we all abanded sadness.\NWe all abanded kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the world is full of hatred.\NThere's no hope, then take this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘で建った塔の　深層で燃える炎
